f old star clusters in M101: a bright population of halo\nclusters and a fainter, possibly younger, population of old disk clusters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Apr 2015 20:25:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-03"}
