adius observed in the extended disks of Milky\nWay-like galaxies only to merger-induced stellar migration.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Apr 2015 14:15:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 30 Apr 2015 09:13:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-01"}
